{"tid":2273524,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"不捨得開心 侵侵將你抱起","createTime":"2020-11-05T21:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T10:16:26.000Z","uid":196948,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a23eec84f656ee8becf12b0bcd795922e76f2c73","tid":2273524,"uid":196948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T21:12:07.000Z","msg":"不捨得開心 侵侵將你抱起<br />\n<br />\n不捨得傷心 留歷史來轉記<br />\n<br />\n以為票數定會升起　會令鬼國討厭你<br />\n<br />\n差點為什麼都忘記  也想選你<br />\n<br />\n緊張的賓洲　一般都不會結果  <br />\n<br />\n幼齒的軀體　仍能給拜登起火<br />\n<br />\n你用殘餘力氣觀摩　證實拜登腦出錯<br />\n<br />\n將兩黨承擔不起的難過<br />\n<br />\n放心鏈過    也許選舉這條路　<br />\n<br />\n開心的報數　不夠票數高攀進內才摔倒  <br />\n<br />\n看著選舉這條路　才令我突然看到　<br />\n<br />\n我的悲哀身份只夠我流淚　不可選到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />訓唔著，是但狗作"},{"pid":"bd6c24fc42ab177445e645137d3501ef3335eb32","tid":2273524,"uid":163199,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T21:14:13.000Z","msg":"開心的步數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎加入教會"},{"pid":"35475e0aaef02ebeec46a25532026bc054ace997","tid":2273524,"uid":208323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T21:14:28.000Z","msg":"Trump 2024"},{"pid":"628b436a8573b5372fb4c5669077608d0c91d943","tid":2273524,"uid":244710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T21:15:38.000Z","msg":"耶和華愛你"},{"pid":"b6409590226b402d5f5eb1991ac4ca0fd73a5efd","tid":2273524,"uid":243854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T21:50:58.000Z","msg":"呢排真係好多教友上連登作歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4d193e761867edd53db6fab445dbb0c49b54cc","tid":2273524,"uid":35193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T22:04:46.000Z","msg":"邊間教會？"},{"pid":"8c31faed1b506254128eb3dc0869cdc1ba65c0cd","tid":2273524,"uid":73989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy"